# Handbook

Root host skill for the `Handbook` family.

- Installed home: `~/handbook/`
- Installed thin projections: `~/handbook/.agents/skills/handbook/` and `~/handbook/.agents/skills/handbook-charter-intake/`
- Codex discovery glue: `~/.codex/skills/handbook*`

This root skill is informational and packaging-oriented. Use `handbook-charter-intake` for the charter intake workflow.

Successful user-global installs refresh these surfaces together:

- `~/handbook/`
- `~/.codex/skills/handbook*`

Preferred install/update paths:

- Tagged release install/update: `scripts/handbook/install.sh`
- Source checkout global install/update: `cargo install --locked --force --path crates/cli && bash tools/codex/install.sh`
- Repo-local projection refresh for development only: `bash tools/codex/generate.sh --repo-local` or `bash tools/codex/install.sh --repo-local`

Do not edit generated projections under `.agents/skills/**` by hand. Edit `install/handbook-home/SKILL.md.tmpl`, `install/handbook-home/agents/openai.yaml`, `install/handbook-home/charter-intake/SKILL.md.tmpl`, or `install/handbook-home/charter-intake/openai.yaml`, then rerun `bash tools/codex/generate.sh`.
